'''第36屆獨立精神獎'''（The 36th Independent Spirit Awards）是獨立電影（Film Independent）組織以茲獎勵[[2020年電影|2020年電影]]與電視劇的獎項。本屆首度增設電視類獎項，以表揚視角獨特、創新與大膽的電視節目<ref name="IFO">{{cite web|url=https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-film-independent-spirit-award-nominations-announced/|title=2021 Film Independent Spirit Award Nominations Announced!|publisher=獨立電影（Film Independent）|author=Matt Warren|date=2021-01-26|accessdate=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126162015/https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-film-independent-spirit-award-nominations-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="air24">{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/2021-spirit-awards-add-television-film-independent-1234589485/|title=2021 Film Independent Spirit Awards Expand to Honor Television|publisher=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|author=Libby Hill|date=2020-09-29|accessdate=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426035912/https://www.indiewire.com/2020/09/2021-spirit-awards-add-television-film-independent-1234589485/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。典禮原定於2021年4月24日舉辦<ref name="air24" />，後提前至4月22日舉行，並於晚間十點（[[北美東部時區|北美東部時區]]）／晚間七點（[[太平洋時區|太平洋時區]]）在{{le|IFC (美國電視頻道)|IFC (American TV channel)|IFC}}直播<ref name="IFO" /><ref name="Deadline">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/independent-spirit-awards-new-date-oscars-2021-1234677604/|title=Independent Spirit Awards Breaks Tradition During Pandemic, Will Take Place Thursday Before Oscars|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2021-01-21|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320020504/https://deadline.com/2021/01/independent-spirit-awards-new-date-oscars-2021-1234677604/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特別獎於3月16日宣布得獎名單<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-spirit-award-grant-winners-announced-take-home-75000-in-filmmaker-support/|title=2021 Spirit Award Grant Winners Announced, Take Home $75,000 in Filmmaker Support|publisher=獨立電影（Film Independent）|author=Matt Warren|date=2021-03-16|accessdate=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323201851/https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/2021-spirit-award-grant-winners-announced-take-home-75000-in-filmmaker-support/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/here-are-the-winners-of-the-2021-film-independent-spirit-award-winners/|title=Here are the Winners of the 2021 Film Independent Spirit Awards!|publisher=獨立電影（Film Independent）|author=Matt Warren|date=2021-04-22|accessdate=2021-04-23|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423080829/https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/here-are-the-winners-of-the-2021-film-independent-spirit-award-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[奧利維亞·魏爾德|奧莉薇亞·魏爾德]]、[[巴里·傑金斯|巴瑞·賈金斯]]與[[拉薇安·考克斯|拉薇安·考克斯]]於2021年1月26日一同在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上宣布入圍名單<ref name="IFO" /><ref name="Deadline" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/independent-spirit-awards-nominations-list-2021|title=Film Independent Spirit Awards: 'Never Rarely Sometimes Always', 'Minari', 'Ma Rainey's Black Bottom', 'Nomadland' Top Nominations|author=Hilary Lewis|date=2021-01-26|work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]]|access-date=2021-01-26|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318224654/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/independent-spirit-awards-nominations-list-2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>，頒獎典禮主持人則由{{le|梅麗莎・維拉塞諾|Melissa Villaseñor}}擔任<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/saturday-night-live-melissa-villasenor-to-host-film-independent-spirit-awards-org-to-feature-directors-close-up-series-1234689538/|title=‘SNL’s Melissa Villaseñor To Host Film Independent Spirit Awards; Org To Feature Directors Close-Up Series|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|date=2021-02-08|work=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222133037/https://deadline.com/2021/02/saturday-night-live-melissa-villasenor-to-host-film-independent-spirit-awards-org-to-feature-directors-close-up-series-1234689538/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/snls-melissa-villasenor-to-host-the-2021-film-independent-spirit-awards-april-22/|title=SNL’s Melissa Villaseñor to Host the 2021 Film Independent Spirit Awards, April 22|publisher=獨立電影（Film Independent）|author=Matt Warren|date=2021-02-08|accessdate=2021-03-22|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211000744/https://www.filmindependent.org/blog/snls-melissa-villasenor-to-host-the-2021-film-independent-spirit-awards-april-22/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

